      <Placemark>
        <name>The Royal Kitchen Bali</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AE5a_GwqpG9rAgzKMgS9r1qiMhrDCPf0OnDEN046qxbpY2EwJRzS6MDkHETxF5vgm2OPncre1luCIjCjp188qGHDmlSou7QgnYjmtZH4qcn9El1DtY-ES-Q2ggmFP7kG3QqgYsoNz3xGcr7DwhMUSHRimUBjjr8VBcAHBLAmzYVOLWu3k9Ia8yygvRZVp2dFVg_RaSFVLcn-1fPgwHlPK_yRIkaB1JIRZfxjtipBpUwAevGnyIpN_YgzpPynHLM?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>好吃的印度料理餐廳，劉燦榮社長大力推薦<br>看「峇里島旅遊攻略」的介紹：https://gobaligo.id/go/nusa-dua-guide]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1899-0288D1</styleUrl>
